title: Mammals and montremes of Porcupine Ridge and Daylesford
description: This album covers mammals and monotremes of Porcupine Ridge and surrounds - to about 30 kilometres, so including Hepburn Regional park and parts of the Wombat State Forest. It includes feeding signs, bones, tracks and scats.

items.title: Hydromys chrysogaster
items.content_text: Two Native Water Rats observed at the creek behind the lake.
